    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and ready for a new home! It runs super smoothly and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures. I've taken great care of it, so you're getting a reliable car that still looks great in the driveway. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
