      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power delivery through individual throttle bodies, with the double-VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and refreshed bushings to maintain the original kinematic precision. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its history, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the high-revving engagement and balanced handling characteristics that define this era of M-division engineering.",
